27#ifndef __RADEON_AUDIO_H__
28#define __RADEON_AUDIO_H__
29
30#include <linux/types.h>
31
32#define RREG32_ENDPOINT(block, reg) \
33 radeon_audio_endpoint_rreg(rdev, (block), (reg))
34#define WREG32_ENDPOINT(block, reg, v) \
35 radeon_audio_endpoint_wreg(rdev, (block), (reg), (v))
36
37struct radeon_audio_basic_funcs
38{
39 u32 (*endpoint_rreg)(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 offset, u32 reg);
40 void (*endpoint_wreg)(struct radeon_device *rdev,
41 u32 offset, u32 reg, u32 v);
42 void (*enable)(struct radeon_device *rdev,
43 struct r600_audio_pin *pin, u8 enable_mask);
44};
45
46struct radeon_audio_funcs
47{
48 void (*select_pin)(struct drm_encoder *encoder);
49 struct r600_audio_pin* (*get_pin)(struct radeon_device *rdev);
50 void (*write_latency_fields)(struct drm_encoder *encoder,
51 struct drm_connector *connector, struct drm_display_mode *mode);
52 void (*write_sad_regs)(struct drm_encoder *encoder,
53 struct cea_sad *sads, int sad_count);
54 void (*write_speaker_allocation)(struct drm_encoder *encoder,
55 u8 *sadb, int sad_count);
56 void (*set_dto)(struct radeon_device *rdev,
57 struct radeon_crtc *crtc, unsigned int clock);
58 void (*update_acr)(struct drm_encoder *encoder, long offset,
59 const struct radeon_hdmi_acr *acr);
60 void (*set_vbi_packet)(struct drm_encoder *encoder, u32 offset);
61 void (*set_color_depth)(struct drm_encoder *encoder, u32 offset, int bpc);
62 void (*set_avi_packet)(struct radeon_device *rdev, u32 offset,
63 unsigned char *buffer, size_t size);
64 void (*set_audio_packet)(struct drm_encoder *encoder, u32 offset);
65 void (*set_mute)(struct drm_encoder *encoder, u32 offset, bool mute);
66 void (*mode_set)(struct drm_encoder *encoder,
67 struct drm_display_mode *mode);
68 void (*dpms)(struct drm_encoder *encoder, bool mode);
69};
70
71int radeon_audio_init(struct radeon_device *rdev);
72void radeon_audio_detect(struct drm_connector *connector,
73 struct drm_encoder *encoder,
74 enum drm_connector_status status);
75u32 radeon_audio_endpoint_rreg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
76 u32 offset, u32 reg);
77void radeon_audio_endpoint_wreg(struct radeon_device *rdev,
78 u32 offset, u32 reg, u32 v);
79struct r600_audio_pin *radeon_audio_get_pin(struct drm_encoder *encoder);
80void radeon_audio_fini(struct radeon_device *rdev);
81void radeon_audio_mode_set(struct drm_encoder *encoder,
82 struct drm_display_mode *mode);
83void radeon_audio_dpms(struct drm_encoder *encoder, int mode);
84unsigned int radeon_audio_decode_dfs_div(unsigned int div);
85
86#endif
